5|$|Fiqh {{literature}} {{describes in}} detail the manners of carrying out the <b>rites</b> <b>of</b> Hajj, and pilgrims generally follow handbooks and expert guides to successfully fulfill the requirements of Hajj. In performing the <b>rites</b> <b>of</b> hajj, the pilgrims not only follow the model of Muhammad, but also commemorate the events associated with Abraham.|$|E
